Metadata.Title: Providence Remnants [pt.1/5]
Metadata.Description: The Constant is dead, but Providence is not. With its leadership removed, some of Providence's high-ranking members scramble to re-establish some modicum of power for themselves.I believe that in time, Providence will reclaim its dominance of global politics and potentially seek reprisal.I've acquired intel that the remaining high-ranking members are hastily withdrawing funds from New York, with assistance from some low-rank initiates.Eliminate them all and we can trace their money.GL, 47
